summary: what do you think of single dad h? what concepts and ideas do you have in your mind, i feel like asking because we all ask you...
question: what do you think of single dad h? what concepts and ideas do you have in your mind, i feel like asking because we all ask you to write what we’d like, but what would you like to write about this topic, or any topic really please don’t feel like i’m pushing you towards writing just about this— it can be any concept you like ♥️
answer:
single dad h struggles here and there but he tries to do it all for his baby angel.

he still has his career of course, but he barely goes out for some late night with the crew. he’d bring his baby daughter with him to the studio and to tour, but she’s gonna have her tantrums sometimes because that isn’t what she wants in that moment but there’s a time baby angel gets passive-agressive.

and it made harry feel guilty to his core, so he takes her home in the middle of a studio session and stayed with her for the rest of the night and for the rest of the week making it up to her.

he may be the one who gets treated like a king in stage and maybe even out but he treats his daughter even more greater than that as he could do like she deserves to be treated as.

he gets his food cooked for him, but he’s the one who makes hers and even feeds her to it, sometimes resorting to airplane and train sounds just to have her finish it.

he has suits custom-made and people who helps him dress up and make it even more perfect, but he’s the one who picks his angel’s outfits, dresses her and teaches her how to use the big toilet bowl now by herself, because she’s three and really precious and smart.

single dad h gets a bit offended when someone says that he should get himself a girl, one who wouldn’t leave him, and he’s not all scoffy because of his ex who gave birth and put all the responsibilities and settled for someone else — but because they think he can’t do it.

he can, not perfectly. but he can.

he’s just finished a show and he’s all sweaty, about to go to the dressing room in where his baby angel was supposed to be asleep in and he definitely hears her giggles a few feet away, and he knows that he has to ask her why she’s still awake.

he opens the door and to his surprise, his angel’s absolutelt energetic and jumping and dancing on the floor, and right in front of her was someone who he reckons is a crew memeber he’s seen a few times — going along with her and he thinks that the name’s y/n.

h’s angel looks up with a grin adorning her face, lip bit in excitement and she’s a bit sweaty but y/n’s taking care of that as she wipes her sweat away and puts a towel on her back so that she wouldn’t get a cold because of the combination of her sweat, the airconditioning, and that it could dry on her.

“daddy — meet y/n!”
